M.D.C. Holdings Inc said it soldsubstantially all the assets of its oil and gas unit, MizelPetro Resources Inc, and affiliated partnerships, for 38 mlndlrs in cash to &lt;Parker and Parsley Petroleum Co>, Midland,Texas.    The company said that, subject to certain post-closingadjustments, it expects to post a small profit on the sale. Reuter&#3;